    startDose: "Combined 40:1 myo + D-chiro for PCOS context: 2g myo + 50mg D-chiro daily, escalate to BID after 2-4 weeks if tolerated. Myo-only for non-PCOS contexts: 1-2g myo-inositol daily, escalate based on use case. High-dose myo for anxiety / OCD: gradual titration to 12g+ daily over 2-3 weeks to assess tolerance.",
